body_html:
Upon further investigation, I found that the file passed as an argument to Zipper.exe (provided by bazel as third_party) had a whole bunch of unnecessary zip files, which I got from:

grep zip= /c/users/nwani/_bazel_nwani/oemicc5z/execroot/org_tensorflow/bazel-out/x64_windows-opt/bin/tensorflow/tools/pip_package/simple_console_for_windows.zip-2.params

After removing all these zip files from the list of files to be zipped, zipper was successful and the build/test process proceeded.

I said that these zip files in the list of files to be zipped are redundant, because their contents were also listed as files to be zipped. The 18 zip files which I removed manually from the params file were:

mnist.zip
linear_regression.zip
rnn_colorbot.zip
rnn_ptb.zip
known_anomaly.zip
lstm.zip
multivariate.zip
predict.zip
offline_analyzer.zip
freeze_graph.zip
import_pb_to_tensorboard.zip
inspect_checkpoint.zip
optimize_for_inference.zip
print_selective_registration_header.zip
saved_model_cli.zip
strip_unused.zip
create_python_api.zip
grpc_tensorflow_server.zip

body:
Upon further investigation, I found that the file passed as an argument to Zipper.exe (provided by bazel as third_party) had a whole bunch of unnecessary zip files, which I got from:
```
grep zip= /c/users/nwani/_bazel_nwani/oemicc5z/execroot/org_tensorflow/bazel-out/x64_windows-opt/bin/tensorflow/tools/pip_package/simple_console_for_windows.zip-2.params
```

After removing all these zip files from the list of files to be zipped, zipper was successful and the build/test process proceeded. 

I said that these zip files in the list of files to be zipped are redundant, because their contents were also listed as files to be zipped. The 18 zip files which I removed manually from the params file were:
```
mnist.zip
linear_regression.zip
rnn_colorbot.zip
rnn_ptb.zip
known_anomaly.zip
lstm.zip
multivariate.zip
predict.zip
offline_analyzer.zip
freeze_graph.zip
import_pb_to_tensorboard.zip
inspect_checkpoint.zip
optimize_for_inference.zip
print_selective_registration_header.zip
saved_model_cli.zip
strip_unused.zip
create_python_api.zip
grpc_tensorflow_server.zip
```
